anyone who FUCKS with jocelyn FUCKS up with me. She is one of the nicest people here in this cruel world we live in, so whoever is talking all this shit about her can burn in hell!!! I dont care who it is. J-Slice, I love you man. I will always be here for you and take the first bullet.

Sky is a retard. I am sitting right next to her right now and talking to her as I am writing this. TEEN GIRL SQUAD!!! SOOOOO GOOD!!!! Sky is not a butt hole though, she is just stupid. But, butt hole or not, she is still my cool buddy. Anyways, I might not be on here again for a few days, maybe even weks because I am grounded off of the internet at my house and I am at school. Oh well, my parents dont know about this, so shhhhh, dont tell them!!!

Hey, i got livejournal! whoo..ok im done. Well, i know a lot of people on here and they tell me about all the interesting stuff on here, so I hought i'd come check it out. J-slice said that some nasty words were exchanged between her and someone else who will not be named, and I wanted to find her. NO ONE makes fun of MY jocelyn and lives to tell about it!!!grrr!!! But, according to Z-Slice, everything is kinda okey dokey between them now...LIES!!! i hope to frickin god that jocelyn is just planning her revenge.
